OL,3,CMother's 'pure desperation' as son
OL,4,Cmissing on Italian island of Sardinia
OL,6,FThe mother of a man from Somerset who
OL,7,Fvanished in Sardinia has made a plea
OL,8,Ffor information on his whereabouts,
OL,9,Fsaying authorities are not doing
OL,10,Fenough to find him.
OL,12,FMichael Frison, 25, from Chard
OL,13,Fdisappeared in the inhospitable Luras
OL,14,Fregion of the Mediterranean island in
OL,15,FJuly 2024.
OL,17,FHe had been visiting his grandparents
OL,18,Fand had decided to go camping with a
OL,19,Ffriend he had met in Sardinia in the
OL,20,Finhospitable Luras region of the
OL,21,Fisland.
