OL,3,CMother's 'pure desperation' as son
OL,4,Cmissing on Italian island of Sardinia
OL,6,FMichael's mother, Cristina Pittalis,
OL,7,Ftold ITV News West Country she was
OL,8,Freturning to the island to resume her
OL,9,Fown one-woman hunt in the absence of
OL,10,FItalian search teams.
OL,12,F"It's what mums do," she said. "It's a
OL,13,Flove that gives you a power to carry
OL,14,Fon and not stop."
OL,16,FShe added: "You just find the courage
OL,17,Fand you're not afraid of anything or
OL,18,Fanyone. I'm not afraid to go against
OL,19,Fthe authorities should it comes to it."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
