OL,3,CMother's 'pure desperation' as son
OL,4,Cmissing on Italian island of Sardinia
OL,6,FChristina is appealing for Michael's
OL,7,Ffriend Naomi, who he met on the
OL,8,Fisland, to get in touch as she
OL,9,Fbelieves he may have information on
OL,10,Fhis whereabouts.
OL,12,FShe said: "I need you, Naomi. I need
OL,13,Fyour help. You've done nothing wrong.
OL,15,F"However, you were the last person to
OL,16,Fbe with Michael. You can still help us
OL,17,Funderstand Michael's state of mind and
OL,18,Fperhaps the reasons behind his
OL,19,Fdisappearance."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
