OL,3,CMother's 'pure desperation' as son
OL,4,Cmissing on Italian island of Sardinia
OL,6,FCristina said the Italian authorities
OL,7,Fare now upgrading the inquiry into
OL,8,FMichael's disappearance, following her
OL,9,Fappeal on the Italian TV show, 'Chi
OL,10,FL'Ha Vista'.
OL,12,F"The authorities are now potentially
OL,13,Fchanging the line of investigation,"
OL,14,FCristina said.
OL,16,F"It's not been officially communicated
OL,17,Fto me but I believe now it will
OL,18,Fprobably be investigated as a crime."
