OL,3,CMother's 'pure desperation' as son
OL,4,Cmissing on Italian island of Sardinia
OL,6,FShe said it's "out of character" for
OL,7,FMichael to have disappeared without
OL,8,Fgetting in touch with his family or
OL,9,Ffriends.
OL,11,F"Michael has not left voluntarily,"
OL,12,Fshe said. "Something must have
OL,13,Fhappened."
OL,15,FCristina has travelled to the island
OL,16,Fsix times since her son disappeared,
OL,17,Fand said it's "very difficult" to keep
OL,18,Fcarrying on.
