OL,6,FShe said: "I am always determined to
OL,7,Ffind out what happened to Michael, and
OL,8,Fpotentially see him again.
OL,10,F"But the majority of time time is pure
OL,11,Fdesperation, and it's impossible to
OL,12,Fcarry on not knowing what has
OL,13,Fhappened."
